      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "5-stage gate per arm (risk-first \u00b7 no alpha):\n  1 Registered  \u2192  2 Backtest-survival\n     (Gate-A: worst-wk DD <25% \u00b7 \u22657 t/wk @0.70%)\n  3 Forward-started \u2192 4 Forward-eligible\n     (7d DD <25% \u00b7 \u22657 t/wk \u00b7 median wk-ret \u22650)\n  5 Operator sign-off (human: STRATEGY_NAME+LIVE)\n\u2192 verdicts (strategy_gates.json) \u00b7 GUARDIAN matrix\n\u2192 risk-first leaderboard \u00b7 default locked \u00b7 no auto-promote",
